data.description: Wonderful end unit townhome. Three bedrooms, three and one half baths. Eat in kitchen, living room dinning room, Beautiful  deck off the living room overlooking a wonderful back yard. Upper level has three bedrooms and two full baths, lots of space. Lower level has a large family room, a full bath, and a wood fireplace.  The backyard is full of plants, flowers and trees. A large laundry room and storage space. A carpet allowance for the master bedroom and the family room of $1500. will allowed This house is close to everything, shopping, schools, buses, metro, playgrounds for the little ones, and downtown Gaithersburg.  Please park in assigned spots, 190 in front of the house or the visitors spots.  Showings 10AM to 5PM.
